article.description: — Isaiah Thompson had 17 points in FGCU's 70-53 victory over Georgia Southern on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Thompson scores 17 in FGCU's victory over Georgia Southern
article.linkText: Thompson scores 17 in FGCU's victory over Georgia Southern
article.story: STATESBORO, Ga. -- — Isaiah Thompson had 17 points in FGCU's 70-53 victory over Georgia Southern on Wednesday night. Thompson added three steals for the Eagles (6-2). Caleb Catto scored 13 points while going 6 of 8 (1 for 3 from distance). Zach Anderson was 3 of 5 shooting and 5 of 6 from the free throw line to finish with 11 points, while adding seven rebounds. The Eagles (4-4) were led in scoring by Jalen Finch, who finished with 16 points. Kaden Archie added 13 points for Georgia Southern. Tai Strickland also had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
